I hope you enjoy this song as much as I do, this is my favorite song from my Upcoming Album “The Sky’s The Limit” coming tomorrow. I’ll still release songs one by one on here!
I have been looking forward to this album since the beginning of January! I have never been so inspired to make music during January.
